data.description: This Charming 4 bedroom 2 bath home the assessor shows 1380 sf but has a 475 sf  permitted enclosed sunroom/living room not included in the square footage  That totals to 1856 sf  of home ,which Features A New roof ,New floors , new paint , a large covered patio with valley and mountain views a dog run ,an oversized 2 car garage w/ work bench plus plenty of space for and RV or Boat. A large .45 ac corner lot w/ mature plants and flowers  This special home really needs to be viewed to appreciate. The private master bath has a shower stall plus a sauna.  The Sauna come with the home AS-Is with no wants or warranties.
